221
00:14:25,728 --> 00:14:28,083
Pode me dar as chaves
da sala dos fundos, Maggie?

222
00:14:28,099 --> 00:14:30,125
- Dos fundos?
- Sim, por favor.

223
00:14:33,708 --> 00:14:34,708
Obrigado.

224
